sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户程序
    participant Lib as libcudart
    participant Driver as libcuda (Driver)
    participant Kernel as nvidia.ko
    participant GPU as GPU 硬件

    User->>Lib: cudaLaunch<<<grid, block>>>(args)
    Lib->>Lib: 解析 args
    Lib->>Driver: cuLaunchKernel()
    Driver->>Driver: 构建 GPU 命令缓冲区
    Driver->>Kernel: ioctl(0x4e, cmd_buf)
    Kernel->>Kernel: 解析命令缓冲区
    Kernel->>Kernel: 推送到 GPU 命令队列
    Kernel->>Kernel: 触发 GPU 调度器
    Kernel->>GPU: GPU 命令
    GPU->>GPU: Warp Scheduler 分配线程块
    GPU->>GPU: SM 执行 SASS 指令
    GPU->>GPU: 内存访问 L1/L2 cache
